Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Thoracic CT
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Characterization' tab

When I select 'Other parenchymal patterns' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding button' is enabled
And 'Mosaic pattern' checkbox is enabled
And 'Curvilinear opacification' checkbox is enabled
And 'Crazy-paving pattern' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Mosaic pattern' checkbox
Then 'Bronchogenic, air trapping' radio button is enabled
And 'Vasogenic' radio button is enabled
And 'Marked' radio button is enabled
And 'Mild' radio button is enabled
